{"tid":1780173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環有逾200人參與活動　紀念半年前發生612事件","createTime":"2019-12-12T07:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T07:20:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cc95d3bd63736628cd4d700192bb0500907089","tid":1780173,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1497294_1_20191212135433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1497294_1_20191212135433.jpg&h=e5f2901d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民發起在中環「和你lunch」活動，紀念半年前發生的6.12事件，有超過200人站在中環環球大廈附近行人天橋，手持寫上「五大訴求」及指控警方濫暴的單張，並高叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n期間有人在橋上張貼宣傳單張，以及向路經的市民派發傳單。"}]}